						<summary>

						<p>Door-post of the entrance into the same temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājakēsarivarman</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Chakravartin Kulōttuṅgachōḷadēva I: Year 41 = 1110—11 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is damaged.</p>						

						<p>This is the original of which a copy was inscribed later on the south wall of the temple and dealt with above in No. 372.</p>						

